  <Notes>
    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>01908400700018</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>"blessing" (NJPS Kraus | Tate | Hossfeld-Zenger) | NRSV NIV REB Dahood "pools" (reading בְּרֵכָה )</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>02001101100004</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>This could refer two things: (a) God's blessing on certain people which reflects on the entire town, or (b) a blessing pronounced by the upright on a town</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="3" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>02604403000052</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>It is not clear whether this refers to a blessing from God as recompense or to a priestly blessing</Content>
    </Note>
